                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The ceremony on the occasion of the signing of the North Atlantic Treaty included
                    remarks by the twelve participating Foreign Ministers and an address by
                    President Truman. For texts of these statements, see Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, April 17, 1949, page 471.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
